something you said to me yesterday

03:55.694 --> 03:56.695
that really bothered me.

03:56.778 --> 03:57.905
What did I say?

03:57.988 --> 04:00.324
You asked me if I was okay.

04:02.117 --> 04:04.328
It doesn't matter if I'm okay.

04:05.078 --> 04:07.581
This is the 200-meter freestyle.

04:07.664 --> 04:11.210
