09:23.397 --> 09:27.985
First of all, again.
I… I just wanna say I'm sorry.

09:28.610 --> 09:29.736
I appreciate that.

09:29.820 --> 09:33.824
And-- And last night
I told my brother he had to leave.

09:33.907 --> 09:36.702
And I sent him back home.
I'm really putting up boundaries.

09:36.785 --> 09:38.704
Bradley, I didn't ask you to do that.

09:38.787 --> 09:42.040
And what we talked about last night.
There's no simple fix for this.

09:42.124 --> 09:43.125
What? For what?

09:43.208 --> 09:47.421
This is a lot to take on
right before I go do a show.

09:47.504 --> 09:49.256
And I need my head in the right place.

09:49.339 --> 09:51.884
Well, now this has put
my head in a wrong place.

09:51.967 --> 09:52.968
-Wha--
-Bradley.

09:53.051 --> 09:54.803
I need to let in hair and makeup.

09:54.887 --> 09:56.805
And there is not enough makeup
in the world

09:56.889 --> 09:58.891
to make me look like I'm enjoying this.

09:59.850 --> 10:00.851
Okay.

10:02.519 --> 10:03.520
Whatever.

10:12.321 --> 10:14.907
Okay, seven seconds! Good show, everybody.

10:14.990 --> 10:17.284
Five, four, three…

10:20.996 --> 10:22.414
-Good show.
-Good show.

10:25.792 --> 10:29.880
