for interruptions to their daily lives.

10:40.849 --> 10:42.392
-Thanks. Hey.
-Hey.

10:42.476 --> 10:44.144
All businesses have been warned they…

10:44.228 --> 10:45.062
Thanks.

10:45.896 --> 10:47.814
Sorry to take back your set.
Here. Come here.

10:49.024 --> 10:51.235
Don't read anything into it. It's not--

10:51.318 --> 10:54.154
Whatever you say.
You're gonna owe me, you know?

10:55.447 --> 10:57.157
So, any sign of her?

10:57.241 --> 10:59.743
No, she just fucking vanished
into thin air.

11:01.119 --> 11:05.207
