11:14.967 --> 11:17.845
-…more on Italy and South Korea.
-Yeah, a fucking morgue.

11:17.928 --> 11:20.681
Don't-- Don't joke like that.
It's not funny.

11:21.640 --> 11:25.227
Why? It's not like it's gonna happen,
and even if it does…

11:25.769 --> 11:27.312
Whatever. She had a good run.

11:31.400 --> 11:33.068
I miss Elmira Chip.

11:33.986 --> 11:37.531
Elmira Chip's dead.
He's in a morgue with Alex.

11:39.116 --> 11:40.200
She'll show up.

11:40.284 --> 11:42.703
Our hearts go out
to everyone affected in Italy…

11:48.083 --> 11:49.084
Thank you.

11:53.213 --> 11:55.549
Do you need anything
before I drive back today?

11:59.469 --> 12:01.346
I don't know. Maybe.

12:02.681 --> 12:03.765
Maybe.

12:06.310 --> 12:07.686
I'm all yours this weekend.

12:07.769 --> 12:09.188
Really?

12:09.271 --> 12:11.315
