13:41.321 --> 13:44.950
This is another success story.
A strong, powerful woman.

13:45.033 --> 13:47.578
Yeah. I mean,
we did hire Alex and Chip back.

13:47.661 --> 13:48.996
Hey, sorry, Gerald.

13:49.079 --> 13:51.290
Your assistant's on line 2.
