15:19.962 --> 15:21.380
And Stella!

15:21.463 --> 15:24.424
I don't care if she's in traction,
get Alex in here!

15:24.508 --> 15:26.176
And that's your latest weather.

15:26.260 --> 15:29.054
That warmer weather's gonna be here
before you know it.

15:29.137 --> 15:30.597
I'm gonna miss winter clothes.

15:30.681 --> 15:32.766
