15:37.229 --> 15:38.480
Bradley, what about you?

15:40.107 --> 15:42.860
Still to come,
Prince Harry's first trip to the UK

15:42.943 --> 15:45.612
since announcing
he was quitting as a senior royal.

15:45.696 --> 15:49.867
