for comment. Said it was a car accident.

16:08.802 --> 16:11.180
That's all we have.
Cory wants Alex to report it.

16:17.853 --> 16:21.231
Gayle, Gordon, Joel, Layla,
come here now, please.

16:26.570 --> 16:28.197
