Thank you so much. Thank you. Go. Go.

16:56.433 --> 16:59.394
-Mia, seriously. You've got this.
-Mia, are you okay?

16:59.478 --> 17:03.357
Yeah. But pull the story on the excerpt
until we know for sure.

17:03.440 --> 17:04.525
Okay.

17:12.406 --> 17:13.951
-Hey.
-Hey. I need to talk to you.

17:14.034 --> 17:14.910
So, I wanted--

17:14.992 --> 17:16.994
