1976 Plymouth Duster.

18:38.243 --> 18:41.371
For security purposes, what's the name
associated with the account?

18:41.455 --> 18:42.998
It's my name, Alex Levy.

18:43.081 --> 18:44.708
Great. How can I help you today?

18:45.959 --> 18:48.712
Well, I'm, uh, trying to make a charge,
and it's not going through.

18:48.795 --> 18:50.547
